    "name": "Rhythm Drum 节奏鼓",
    "steam_appid": 3233820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233820/extras/2f28699d4bc4aff323099ca2ddabf5d7.webp?t=1747035395\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Rhythm Drum》是一款充满活力的节奏游戏，玩家将通过鼠标和键盘敲击虚拟鼓点来跟随动感的音乐节拍。游戏提供了多种音乐风格和难度等级，从简单的流行音乐到复杂的电子节拍，每一种曲目都要求玩家精准打击，挑战反应速度和节奏感。玩家可以逐步解锁新的挑战、提高分数。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>*功能介绍*</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超过80种关卡选择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超过8种可解锁的头像和技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-鼠标与键盘的综合使用</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁更多困难关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
